txt.en: 'Hullo! Would you like to be an \qAcquaintance\q of the Rangers of Esteldín? Well look no further! Completion of this quest should do that just for you.\n\n'If this sounds good to you, speak to me again!'
'Alright, soon the Rangers of Esteldín will consider you an Acquaintance. Ready?'
North Downs - Rangers of Esteldín I
By completing this quest, you will be considered an Acquaintance of the Rangers of Esteldín.
